long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: PSA Autocomplete is an application that automatically completes the PSA form. Its objective is simple, the user enters their weekly hours on the extension's options page then when they browse the PSA site a button suggests applying the model. Then, the information entered by the user is injected into the form available on the PSA website. No data is transmitted to third parties or disseminated.
